---
import ExhibitionLayout from '../../layouts/ExhibitionLayout.astro';
import ExhibitionMasthead from '../../components/ExhibitionMasthead.astro';
---
<ExhibitionLayout title="PRIVACY · The Keepers · SF Times" active="home">
  <ExhibitionMasthead slot="masthead" title="PRIVACY" subscript="WHAT WE DON'T COLLECT" cutouts={[]} />
  <article class="ex-prose">
    <p class="ex-prose__eyebrow">NO TRACKING · NO AD PIXELS · NO SOCIAL TRACKERS</p>
    <h1 class="ex-prose__title">WHAT WE COLLECT.<br>WHAT WE DON'T.</h1>
    <p>We don't track you. No analytics on individual pages. No third-party ad pixels. No social-media trackers. Newsletter subscribers give us their email, which we store with our newsletter provider and use only to send the saturday issue. That's it.</p>
  </article>
</ExhibitionLayout>
